## 💻 Local Development

For running locally with Docker:

```bash
# Start all services
docker compose up --build

# Stop all services
docker compose down

# Stop and remove data
docker compose down -v
```

Make sure your local `client/.env` points to localhost:
```
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

And `server/.env` uses either local Mongo or Atlas URI.

