## ⚠️ Common Errors & Fixes

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `Failed to fetch` | Wrong API URL or CORS | Check `VITE_API_BASE_URL` and CORS config |
| `NetworkError` | CORS blocking request | Add Vercel URL to `allowedOrigins` in server.js |
| `E11000 duplicate key` | Old MongoDB index conflict | Drop old indexes in Atlas → Collections → Indexes |
| 404 on page refresh | Missing vercel.json rewrite | Add rewrite rule pointing to `/index.html` |
| Render slow first load | Free tier spins down | Expected — upgrade to $7/mo for always-on |

---

## 💡 Tips

- **Render free tier** spins down after 15 min inactivity — first request takes ~30 sec to wake up
- **Never commit `.env` files** to GitHub — add them to `.gitignore`
- **Environment variables** in Vercel must start with `VITE_` to be accessible in the browser
- For always-on free backend, consider **Koyeb** as an alternative to Render
